data.description: Charming residence nestled in the heart of Arlington in an established quiet neighborhood. Open concept kitchen with bar top seating and breakfast nook overlooking the living area, lots of natural light, wood burning fireplace and an additional living room perfect for entertainment. Bedrooms are located in second floor. Master bedroom has a private balcony. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your dream home!
